title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Anandi gets the chance to meet her teacher. She's extremely glad and also terrified to tell her teacher that she has quit studying.All the family members come together for Gehna's baby shower.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Sandhya finds burnt books and ashes from Anandi's room. Sandhya tries to find out the truth from everybody. Daadisa refuses to agree that she is the reason behind everything.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Shyam's mother tells Shyam to take care of Sugna as she is not in town. Dadiji reminds Gehna about her promise of leaving the house. Sumitra asks Anandi not to hide any truth from her.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Basant apologizes for his mistake to Gehna, but she is upset about Dadiji's taunts. Dadiji goes to the temple. Basant meets Niranjan and discusses about Gehna's interest in music.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Gehna tells Sumitra about her promise of leaving the house, while Basant overhears. Sugna gives Asha a radio, so that she can listen to music to spend time. Basant regrets his bad behaviour.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Basant tells Gehna to take proper care of herself and the child because he is going to take care of everything. Niranjan visits the mansion in Kalyani's absence to give music lessons to Gehna.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Sumitra hides the music teacher, Niranjan from Kalyani. Anandi almost reveals about it to her. Shyam's uncle bribes the doctor to give the wrong injection to Sugna, but Asha stops her from taking it.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Asha tells Sugna that Shyam's uncle wanted to poison her body through the injection. Gehna learns that her father is getting her under age sister married. Basant helps her to stop the wedding.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Gehna isn't able to take her parents' tantrums and faints. She is rushed to the hospital which makes Jagdish and Anandi think that Gehna has entered into labour. Kalyani is scared to lose the child.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Gehna is critical and the doctor can save either her or her child. Basant shocks Kalyani by deciding to save Gehna's life. Kalyani feels humiliated as she thinks that Basant disrespected her.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Basant goes to Kalyani and informs her that the doctor managed to save both, the mother and the child. It's a touching moment for the whole family. Jagdish and Anandi dance in happiness.
